{"id":59989,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/房地产-为楼市降温-北京市完善土地招拍挂制度/","date":"2010-04-17T06:00:20Z","modified":"2010-04-17T06:00:20Z","title":"[房地产] 为楼市降温 北京市完善土地招拍挂制度","content":"<div style=\"float:left;width:28px;color:#c74b15;border:0px solid #000000;margin:0px 0px 0px 0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 0px;line-height:140%;font-size:28px;font-weight:bolder\">据</div>\n<p>新华社报导，北京市周五推出一系列完善土地招拍挂制度的新举措，率先采取行动，响应中国国务院提出的为房地产市场降温的指示。</p>\n<p>报导称，根据修改后的规定，在土地拍卖过程中，市政府官员将评估包括价格在内的多个因素，采用“综合条件最优者得”的综合评标方式。</p>\n<p>报导称，政府拟将开发建设周期、参与建设的政策性住房规模和对未来商品住房销售价格的承诺等因素作为评标条件。</p>\n<div>\n<div style=\"border-top:4px solid #b0cada;margin:12px 5px 3px 0px;font-size:14px;padding:3px 0px 0px 3px;font-weight:bold;color:#303030\">相关阅读</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100415/bch180934.asp?source=article\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"margin:12px 5px 5px 5px;padding-left:8px;background:no-repeat left;font-size:14px;color:#093d72\">中国将二套房贷最低首付比例上调至50%</a> <span style=\"color:#666;font-size:12px;font-family:arial\">2010-04-15</span><br /><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100414/bch105653.asp?source=article\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"margin:12px 5px 5px 5px;padding-left:8px;background:no-repeat left;font-size:14px;color:#093d72\">中国3月份大中城市房价加速上涨</a> <span style=\"color:#666;font-size:12px;font-family:arial\">2010-04-14</span><br /><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100409/CWS185930.asp?source=article\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"margin:12px 5px 5px 5px;padding-left:8px;background:no-repeat left;font-size:14px;color:#093d72\">财经点评：房地产调控地方倒逼中央？</a> <span style=\"color:#666;font-size:12px;font-family:arial\">2010-04-09</span><br /><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100408/rea161955.asp?source=article\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"margin:12px 5px 5px 5px;padding-left:8px;background:no-repeat left;font-size:14px;color:#093d72\">中国房市需求上扬 政策风险仍存</a> <span style=\"color:#666;font-size:12px;font-family:arial\">2010-04-08</span></div>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[9729,9359]}